<h2 id="introduction">1. Introduction</h2>

<p>Soli is a modern, statically-typed programming language designed for clarity and expressiveness. It combines object-oriented programming with functional concepts like the pipeline operator.</p>

<h3>Key Features</h3>

<ul>
    <li><strong>Static Typing with Inference</strong>: Type safety without verbose annotations</li>
    <li><strong>Pipeline Operator</strong>: Chain function calls for readable data transformation</li>
    <li><strong>Object-Oriented Programming</strong>: Classes, inheritance, and interfaces</li>
    <li><strong>Pattern Matching</strong>: Powerful destructuring and matching capabilities</li>
</ul>

